        <h1>First-Time Donor Conversion: Turning One-Time Gifts into Lifelong Supporters</h1>
        <div class="art-meta">
            <span>April 6, 2026</span>
            <span class="art-meta-dot"></span>
            <span>10 min read</span>
        </div>
    </div>
