        <p>Fund-Raise automatically segments first-time donors from your data and tracks their conversion in real time. The donor retention dashboard shows first-time donor retention as a separate KPI, alongside overall and repeat retention. You can see exactly how many of last year&rsquo;s new donors have given again &mdash; and how many haven&rsquo;t.</p>

